Hi jialin, your json format is incorrect so I can not follow what you are concerning ...

(minor) Json uses ":" rather than "=";
(major) Json does not support

{
"value" : { 
  [1, 2], 
  [3, 4]
 }
}
(You can find the markdown render has label the error in red)
As "[]" is an array and "{}" is an object, everything in "{}" should be key-value pair.
So, the correct json is:
{
	"device": "root.sg.d1",
	"timestamp": "150423423423",
	"measurements": ["s1", "s2"],
	"values": {
		"s1": [5.0, "4.0"],
		"s2": [6.0, "7.0"]
	}
}
